  "caption": "In November 2022, GPT 3.5 launched ChatGPT and changed everything.\n\nThree years and four months later, GPT 5.4 can autonomously run multi hour coding sessions, reason through graduate level science, and orchestrate complex workflows across tools.\n\nHere is the full evolution:\n\n2022 \u2192 GPT 3.5: The chatbot that started it all\n2023 \u2192 GPT 4: Multimodal, creative, reliable\n2024 \u2192 GPT 4o + o1: Free intelligence + reasoning chains\n2025 \u2192 GPT 5 series: Agentic workflows arrive\n2026 \u2192 GPT 5.4: Frontier coding, reasoning, and tool use in one model\n\nEvery 6 months, a new leap.\n\nThe models that seemed revolutionary become baselines. The capabilities that felt impossible become table stakes.\n\nIf you are building anything in tech, understanding this pace is not optional. It is survival.\n\n#AI #OpenAI #GPT #LLM #AITimeline #TechEvolution",
